<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>NeuralBridge SDK 中文控制台 / 数据面板</title>
  <meta name="description" content="NeuralBridge SDK 中文控制台与数据面板，展示性能、产品、社区与系统状态指标。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com" />
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css"
    referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0A0A1A;
      --bg-soft: #101228;
      --panel: rgba(16, 18, 40, 0.82);
      --panel-2: rgba(20, 24, 52, 0.92);
      --line: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25);
      --text: #eef2ff;
      --muted: #a8b0d3;
      --cyan: #00E5FF;
      --indigo: #6366F1;
      --green: #22c55e;
      --yellow: #f59e0b;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.08), 0 10px 50px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-sm: 14px;
      --container: 1280px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "Noto Sans SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.10), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.16), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0A1A 0%, #0A0A1A 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 36px 36px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 45%, transparent 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: .45;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--container));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(10, 10, 26, 0.72);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      min-height: 74px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,229,255,0.16), rgba(99,102,241,0.22));
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.25);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,229,255,0.08), 0 0 20px rgba(99,102,241,0.18);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .brand-text {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .nav a {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: .25s ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 34px 0 22px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .9fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-card,
    .status-panel,
    .section-card,
    .metric-card,
    .footer-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(16,18,40,0.86), rgba(12,14,30,0.95));
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 28px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      right: -60px;
      top: -60px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,229,255,0.18), transparent 68%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.18);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: .86rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .hero-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.18);
      color: #dbe5ff;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    .status-panel {
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .panel-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .panel-title h2,
    .section-heading h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .clock {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .clock-date {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

    .status-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .status-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .status-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .status-value {
      font-weight: 700;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(34,197,94,.7);
      display: inline-block;
      animation: pulse 1.8s infinite;
    }

    .uptime {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .uptime-bar {
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .uptime-fill {
      width: 99.98%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--indigo));
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,229,255,.3);
    }

    .uptime-text {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .88rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .sections {
      padding: 12px 0 28px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .section-card {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .section-meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .section-title-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .section-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.22);
      color: var(--cyan);
    }

    .metrics-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .metric-card {
      padding: 18px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform .22s ease, border-color .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease;
    }

    .metric-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,229,255,0.08), 0 18px 40px rgba(99,102,241,0.16);
    }

    .metric-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -20px -40px auto;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99,102,241,0.15), transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .metric-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .metric-icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,229,255,0.12), rgba(99,102,241,0.20));
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.18);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 16px rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
    }

    .metric-label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
      min-height: 46px;
    }

    .metric-value {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--text);
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .metric-value .suffix {
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .metric-desc {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .9rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 0 0 34px;
    }

    .footer-card {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .footer-note strong {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .glow {
      color: var(--cyan);
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; }
      70% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.7; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .metrics-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .topbar-inner {
        padding: 12px 0;
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .nav {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }
      .hero {
        padding-top: 22px;
      }
      .hero-card,
      .status-panel,
      .section-card,
      .footer-card {
        border-radius: 16px;
      }
      .hero-card,
      .status-panel,
      .section-card {
        padding: 18px;
      }
      .metrics-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .clock {
        font-size: 1.55rem;
      }
      .metric-label {
        min-height: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container topbar-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-badge">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <div class="brand-title">NeuralBridge SDK 中文控制台</div>
          <div class="brand-subtitle">实时数据面板 / Console Dashboard</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <nav class="nav" aria-label="主导航">
        <a href="#performance">性能指标</a>
        <a href="#product">产品指标</a>
        <a href="#community">社区指标</a>
        <a href="#system">系统状态</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square"></i>
            基于基准测试与官方 API 的真实指标
          </div>
          <h1>NeuralBridge SDK 数据总览</h1>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            本控制台集中展示 NeuralBridge SDK 的性能、产品、社区与系统状态数据。
            页面采用深色科技风设计，支持响应式布局、实时钟表显示以及指标数字滚动动画，
            适合用于 SDK 官网、产品控制台或演示看板。
          </p>
          <div class="hero-tags">
            <span class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i> 微秒级延迟</span>
            <span class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-box"></i> 轻量级 SDK</span>
            <span class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> 故障注入验证</span>
            <span class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> 实时数据展示</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="status-panel" id="system">
          <div>
            <div class="panel-title">
              <h2>系统状态</h2>
              <span class="eyebrow" style="margin:0; padding:6px 10px;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish"></i> Live
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="clock" id="clock">--:--:--</div>
            <div class="clock-date" id="clockDate">---- 年 -- 月 -- 日</div>
          </div>

          <div class="status-list">
            <div class="status-item">
              <div class="status-label">服务状态</div>
              <div class="status-value"><span class="dot"></span> 在线</div>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
              <div class="status-label">延迟状态</div>
              <div class="status-value"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle glow"></i> 正常（&lt;5ms）</div>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
              <div style="width:100%;">
                <div class="status-label">服务正常运行时间指示器</div>
                <div class="uptime">
                  <div class="uptime-bar" aria-label="服务正常运行时间">
                    <div class="uptime-fill"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="uptime-text">
                    <span>当前可用性</span>
                    <strong>99.98%</strong>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sections">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-card" id="performance">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
              <div class="section-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-microchip"></i></div>
              <div>
                <h2>性能指标组</h2>
                <div class="section-meta">来自基准测试数据</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-meta">关注微秒级处理能力与吞吐表现</div>
          </div>

          <div class="metrics-grid">
            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-stethoscope"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">故障诊断 P50</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="22" data-decimals="0">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">µs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">1M 样本条件下的中位响应时间。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">故障诊断 P99</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="47" data-decimals="0">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">µs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">1M 样本条件下的高分位延迟表现。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">熔断检查 P50</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="0.4" data-decimals="1">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">µs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">1M 样本下熔断逻辑的超低开销检查时间。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">遥测吞吐量</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="177582" data-decimals="0" data-format="int">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">rec/s</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">单线程条件下的记录处理吞吐能力。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-timeline"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">遥测延迟</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="5.6" data-decimals="1">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">µs/record</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">单条遥测记录处理的平均延迟。</div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-card" id="product">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
              <div class="section-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-cube"></i></div>
              <div>
                <h2>产品指标组</h2>
                <div class="section-meta">SDK 体积、依赖与验证规模</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-meta">轻量、简洁、工程化可用</div>
          </div>

          <div class="metrics-grid">
            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-box-open"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">SDK 大小</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="suffix">~</span>
                <span class="counter" data-target="375" data-decimals="0">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">KB</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">适合快速集成与高效分发的轻量包体积。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">依赖数</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="1" data-decimals="0">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">（httpx）</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">核心依赖极少，便于维护与部署。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-virus"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">故障注入验证</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="70000" data-decimals="0" data-format="int">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">次</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">覆盖 7 种故障类型的验证测试规模。</div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-card" id="community">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div class="section-title-wrap">
              <div class="section-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i></div>
              <div>
                <h2>社区指标组</h2>
                <div class="section-meta">来自公开社区与发行平台数据</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-meta">观察下载热度与项目关注度</div>
          </div>

          <div class="metrics-grid">
            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
                <div class="metric-icon"><i class="fa-brands fa-python"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-label">PyPI 月下载</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <span class="counter" data-target="13769" data-decimals="0" data-format="int">0</span>
                <span class="suffix">次</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-desc">最近月度下载量，反映社区活跃度与使用趋势。</div>
            </article>

            <article class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-top">
